# Production API base (used by `vite build`).
# All-on-Vercel: the FastAPI backend is served same-origin under /api.
# If you host the backend elsewhere (e.g. Render), override this in the Vercel
# project's Environment Variables — e.g. VITE_API_URL=https://lendlens-api.onrender.com
VITE_API_URL=/api
